snippet.title: Age of Wonders 3
snippet.description:
Age of Wonders 3, the long-awaited continuation of the hit strategy series available DRM-free on GOG.com.

See the in-depth gemeplay footage from the current alpha build:
http://youtu.be/KL_fhkSgwfs
